<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About Us | Pathshala</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- Google Font & Font Awesome -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a2e0f1f0c3.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #43cea2, #185a9d);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    .about-section {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #185a9d;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-around;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .feature {
      width: 250px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .feature i {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #4caf50;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .feature h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #185a9d;
    }

    .about-image {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    footer {
      background: #333;
      color: #eee;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .features {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .feature {
        width: 80%;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .about-section {
        margin: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
      <%-include("./include/navbar.ejs")%>
<section class="about-section">
  <h2>About Pathshala</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Pathshala</strong> is a modern and intuitive student management system created for tuition centers and educational institutions. 
    Our platform is built to simplify the process of enrolling students, tracking fees, maintaining academic records, and streamlining communication.
  </p>
  <p>
    Designed with educators and administrators in mind, Pathshala brings powerful features into a clean, responsive interface. 
    Whether you're running a small coaching center or a large academy, our tool adapts to your needs.
  </p>

  <img class="about-image" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf" alt="About Pathshala">

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
      <h3>Smart Admissions</h3>
      <p>Quickly register students with just a few clicks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <i class="fas fa-money-check-alt"></i>
      <h3>Fee Tracking</h3>
      <p>Stay on top of all monthly payments and dues.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
      <h3>Progress Overview</h3>
      <p>Monitor student progress and keep records organized.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Pathshala â€” Empowering Education Digitally
</footer>

</body>
</html>
